text:
Wednesday's girls' cross country roundup: Gettle leads York Suburban's victory GameTimePA.com staff Posted: 10/01/2015 09:50:08 PM EDT Girls' cross country 
YORK SUBURBAN SWEEPS AT HOME >> York Suburban's Olivia Gettle finished first in 20:19.74, nearly a full minute ahead of the second-place finisher, as the Trojans defeated Dallastown and York Catholic at home. 
Christian School of York's Nicole Shelton finished second, one of two Crusaders in the race, in 21:04.77 before Dallastown's Haley Brown (21:18.36) rounded out the top three. 3.1 miles at York Suburban 
York Suburban 26, Dallastown 31 York Suburban 15, York Catholic 50 Dallastown 16, York Catholic 43
